cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image synthesis and 3D modeling, which are topics commonly found in the computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The use of generative models and unsupervised learning also suggests a potential fit for the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on modeling in 3D space and evaluating various 3D representations suggests a potential fit for the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
